Package parser

Class AbstractEntryFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.AbstractEntryFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArticleEntryFactory, BookEntryFactory, BookletEntryFactory, InbookEntryFactory, IncollectionEntryFactory, InproceedingsEntryFactory, ManualEntryFactory, MastersthesisEntryFactory, MiscEntryFactory, PhdthesisEntryFactory, ProceedingsEntryFactory, TechreportEntryFactory, UnpublishedEntryFactory
    public abstract class AbstractEntryFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class is the most important part of the parsing process. Here the given entry is being adapted to HashMaps of required and optional Attributes. Every entry also gets bonus variables depending on designed Visitors so that every Visitor class is easy and readable. Such manner makes it easy to add new Visitors just by adding appropriate variable to each entry.
